<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7937274>
    dc:description "FIGURES 19 & 20. Taxa recognized within Longigula Qiu, Zhang & Li, 1983. 19. Longigula auris Qiu, Zhang & Li, 1983, ventral view, redrawn from Qiu et al. (1983, fig. 1). 20. Longigula papillus Qiu, Zhang & Li, 1983, ventral view, redrawn from Qiu et al. (1983, fig. 4). Abbreviations: AT, anterior testis; Ce, cecum; CP, cirrus-pouch; Es, esophagus; GP, genital pore; Me, metraterm; OS, oral sucker; Ov, ovary; Ph, pharynx; PL, papillate lobes; PP, pars prostatica; PT, posterior testis; SR, seminal receptacle; SV, seminal vesicle; Ut, uterus; VF, vitelline follicle; VL, ventrolateral lappets; VS, ventral sucker. Scale bars: Fig. 19 = 1,000 µm; Fig. 20 = 1,000 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7937274/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

